Program: Discovery
Title: Complex molecular systems - and a new metal
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwfr
Last Broadcast Date: 03 May 1995
A new metal which could be cast itself into shape. The programme features a vision of new type of metal, courtesy of Professor George Whitesides, who is discovering the extraordinary power of molecules that can pull themselves into robust lines. Presenter: Roland Pease.